            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>When the meatballs are almost ready, slice your <strong>ciabatta[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Remove the tray[s] with the<strong> </strong>chips from the oven and move them to one side, add the <strong>ciabatta halves </strong>to the other side and return to the oven for 2-3 min or until they’re hot and crusty</p>",
